| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2487 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a83878e9-1779-51b2-bd0b-1dab061e3cdd"
